    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, it is in stunning, showroom-ready shape! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014always garaged, hand-washed only, and strictly maintained. It drives like a dream and the interior still feels brand new. You really won't find another one this clean out there. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
      "price": 43500.0,
