    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional specimen of the E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six power plant. This vehicle boasts surgical mechanical precision, with the dual-VANOS system and individual throttle bodies operating in perfect synchronicity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, sending power through a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critically, the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced, ensuring chassis rigidity under high lateral loads. With documented rod bearing service and a flawless factory finish, this is a turn-key collector\u2019s piece for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
