      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in breathtaking, showroom-fresh condition. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from even the slightest swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains immaculate; the premium leather still carries that distinctive factory aroma, and every surface\u2014from the hand-stitched dashboard to the high-traffic touchpoints\u2014shows zero signs of use. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been maintained with an open-checkbook philosophy and accompanied by a complete, documented service history. Every feature, button, and electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This isn't just a used car; it is a meticulously curated piece of automotive excellence for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
